metadata.name: angel in her room
metadata.description:
Angels, no matter how winged they may be, remain in love.
 They care about those around them. With wings that can save themselves from this unwanted situation, they care about their surroundings, girls, sons, husbands, parents and everyone.
 How many wings do they break.
How many hearts do they break.
He will participate with you in all the hardships of your life and all your misfortunes and joys with you

size : 2400 & 3800 px
